HEADWORD: nondecisive
<hw>nondecisive</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>not crucial; not comprising a
decisive factor in a result. Opposite of <ant>crucial</ant> and
<ant>decisive</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> noncrucial, unimportant.</syn>⟦br⟧
